  emission_level FLOAT
);

);

);

CREATE TABLE sustainability_goals (id INT PRIMARY KEY, goal_name TEXT, target TEXT, completion_date DATE)

CREATE TABLE environmental_impact (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name TEXT, description TEXT, impact_type TEXT)

CREATE TABLE sustainability_initiatives (id INT PRIMARY KEY, initiative_name TEXT, description TEXT, start_date DATE, end_date DATE)

CREATE TABLE sustainability_metrics (id INT PRIMARY KEY, metric_name TEXT, description TEXT, target_value FLOAT, actual_value FLOAT)</t><s>INSERT INTO environmental_impact (id, name, description, impact_type) SELECT 1, 'Carbon Emissions', 'Description of carbon emissions', 'Environmental'</s>

CREATE TABLE sustainability_progress (id INT PRIMARY KEY, initiative_id INT, metric_id INT, progress_value FLOAT, date_recorded DATE)

CREATE TABLE sustainability_metrics (id INT PRIMARY KEY, metric_name TEXT, description TEXT, target_value FLOAT, actual_value FLOAT)</t><s>insert into sustainability_goals (id, goal_name, target, completion_date) select 1, 'reduce carbon footprint', '50%', '2022-12-31'</s>

CREATE TABLE sustainability_initiatives (id INT PRIMARY KEY, initiative_name TEXT, description TEXT, start_date DATE, end_date DATE)

CREATE TABLE sustainability_metrics (id INT PRIMARY KEY, metric_name TEXT, description TEXT, target_value FLOAT, actual_value FLOAT)

CREATE TABLE sustainability_goals (id INT PRIMARY KEY, goal_name TEXT, target TEXT, completion_date DATE)</t><s>INSERT INTO sustainability_goals (id, goal_name, target, completion_date) SELECT 1, 'Reduce Carbon Footprint', '50%', '2022-12-31'</s>

CREATE TABLE sustainability_initiatives (id INT PRIMARY KEY, initiative_name TEXT, description TEXT, start_date DATE, end_date DATE)

CREATE TABLE sustainability_goals (id INT PRIMARY KEY, goal_name TEXT, target TEXT, completion_date DATE)

CREATE TABLE sustainability_metrics (id INT PRIMARY KEY, metric_name TEXT, description TEXT, target_value FLOAT, actual_value FLOAT)</t><s>insert into sustainability_goals (id, goal_name, target, completion_date) select 1, 'reduce carbon footprint', '50%', '2022-12-31'</s>
